				<td colspan="2"><span>first thing to understand is that no matter what you do, you will sometimes lag.
<br />

<br />
second thing is figure out what kind of lag it is..
<br />

<br />
is it..
<br />

<br />

<br />
A)  Nerwork Lag (aka, the &quot;lag-o-meter&quot; on the upper left side of the screen is showing hte lag, and you can move arround fine when lagging, but might be dead when it clears up)
<br />

<br />
B) Computer Lag ( &quot;stuttering&quot; turns, freezing when the AE lands, ect)
<br />

<br />

<br />
give us more information on the kind of lag and we can do mroe to help =)
<br />

<br />
</span></td>
