				<td colspan="2"><span>EQ is very processor and memory bound.
<br />

<br />
Check your MB make and model, find out how fast you can go processor wise and how much memory, and the TYPE of memory, you can use.
<br />
Then use pricewatch or newegg and see what is cheaper for you to get.
<br />
Installing a new CPU or memory is very easy, you can order it and snap it in yourself</span></td>
